{"word":"συστροφή","slug":"συστροφή","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>συστροφή</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <a href='S:συστρέφω'><el>συστρέφω</el></a>\n<el>(συστροφή, ἡ,) </el><p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>a dense mass</i> of men, <i>a gathering</i> of people, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>a sudden storm</i>, <b><a href='S:Polybius'>Polyb.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}